msgstr "虽然这种行为在大多数情况下是有益的，但也有可能会失败，或者列可能会被映射到默认情况下没有提出的字段。"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:195
msgid ""
"If this happens, check the :guilabel:`Show fields of relation fields "
